---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Rubadue Wire | Wire & Cable Solutions"
  description="Since 1977, Rubadue Wire has been pioneering wire solutions with cutting-edge technology, specializing in triple-insulated wire and Litz wire. As a 100% employee-owned company, we solve wire and cable challenges when high performance and reliability are critical."
  category="About"
  eyebrow="About"
  headerTitle="Our Story"
>
  <div class="py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      {/* Description Section */}
      <div class="mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg/8">
          We solve wire and cable challenges when high performance and
          reliability are critical. As a 100% employee-owned company, we are
          committed to innovation, quality, and exceptional customer service.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Mission & Vision Section */}
      <div class="my-12 sm:my-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-primary/20 bg-card text-card-foreground shadow"
          >
            <div
              class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/40 via-primary to-primary/40"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3
                class="flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight mb-6"
              >
                <Target className="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
                Our Mission
              </h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
                We solve wire and cable challenges when high performance and
                reliability are critical.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-primary/20 bg-card text-card-foreground shadow"
          >
            <div
              class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/40 via-primary to-primary/40"
            >
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3
                class="flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-semibold leading-none tracking-tight mb-6"
              >
                <Eye className="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
                Our Vision
              </h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
                Create the premier brand in developing and manufacturing
                specialty wire and cable to support tomorrow's innovation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="my-12 border-t border-primary/10" />

      {/* Built for Performance Section */}
      <div class="my-12 sm:my-16">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl lg:mx-0 mb-10 sm:mb-16">
          <p class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-primary font-display mb-2">
            Why Rubadue
          </p>
          <h2
            class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground"
          >
            Built for Performance. Backed by Partnership.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 sm:mt-6 text-base sm:text-lg/8 text-muted-foreground">
            Rubadue wire powers the products that push today's technology
            forward.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-muted-foreground max-w-4xl">
            When engineers face complex wire and cable challenges, they turn to
            Rubadue for support that goes beyond the spool. From initial design
            to manufacturing at scale, we bring technical design expertise,
            trusted manufacturing, high quality, and responsive partnership â€“ so
            you can deliver with confidence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Design</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-3">
                Solve your size, resistance, partial discharge, and extreme
                environmental challenges
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                We start with your specifications and help design teams manage
                difficult wire and cable specs, from rudimentary to incredibly
                complicated.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div
                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
